qwerty.translation[0].definitions[0].def: a qwerty keyboard on a computer or typewriter has the keys arranged in the usual way for English-speaking countries, with Q, W, E, R, T, and Y on the top row
qwerty.translation[1].definitions[0].def: a qwerty KEYBOARD on a computer or TYPEWRITER has keys arranged in the usual way for English-speaking countries, with the letters Q-W-E-R-T-Y on the top row
